(4, 'About US', 'about-us', '<p>Study Metro is a professional&nbsp;<a href="http://www.studymetro.com/Why_Choose_Us.php"><strong>education consultancy firm</strong></a>, extending excellent support and service to students all over India and gives unlimited study opportunities across the Globe. Our aim is to improve educational standards. Scores of parents have sought our advice to find suitable Universities for their children.</p>\r\n<p>Study Metro helps students to make the right overseas education decisions. Our expertise in the field of overseas education has made us a time-tested resource in helping students to gain admission for suitable courses in recognized universities across the globe. Choosing a University is one of the most difficult decisions a student faces in his life. We not only offer quality education, but also help students to develop the required skills needed for admission.</p>\r\n<p>We establish strong working relationship with foreign educational institutions for the proper placement of our client students. Our intent is to place the right student into the right institution for the right reason.</p>\r\n<p>In order for you to make the best &amp; the right choice, we study your case on the basis Via personal contact with the parent''s and the students and recommend the most appropriate college, University and programs corresponding to the Desires , Ability and Motivation.</p>\r\n<p>We work diligently to provide our students with a "One stop solution to foreign education". We are one of the leading education consultancy firms in India, which is renowned, reputable, trustworthy, caring and professional education consultancy, where students &amp; working professionals can avail all overseas education related services at one stop for the admission and visa process for abroad Universities. Our industry experts and trained counselors help students to select the right destination and appropriate qualification according to their previous qualification and experience.</p>\r\n<p>We believe in the core value underlying our philosophy of the very word Confluence. It is therefore our responsibility to ensure that the organization is managed in a manner that protects and furthers the interests of all our associates Employees, Students, Fellow Consultants &amp; Institutions.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>"When educating the minds of our youth, we must not forget to educate their hearts."</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>&nbsp;</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em><iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/190513423?title=0&amp;byline=0" width="425" height="350" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></em></strong></p>\r\n<h1>Study Metro Affordably Redefining Overseas Education</h1>\r\n<h2>Study Metro is one of the most successful education consulting firms in India today. The firm guides its clients in its own unique way and offers students, programs in colleges of their choice.</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Study Metro is a Study Abroad Consultant having office in Bangalore and Indore, We are the Top Overseas Education Consultants in Bangalore and Indore and received so many awards from recognise body in India and abroad. We provide 24*7 Live chat support to our international students, Who are looking for Abroad Education consultants. We provide abroad education consultancy services like Preparing documents, shortlisting universities and visa training for higher visa success.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>We are the Top Educational Consultancy websites, who has put as much information about courses and universities information over the net so students can find suitable programs. If you Looking for Best Study Abroad Consultants in Bangalore and Indore, You can contact Study Metro Expert Advisor by calling 8088-867-867, 7722-867-867</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Study Metro will help you to find Study Abroad Programs for International students for higher foreign education to shortlist Abroad Universities and will also help to get Scholarships and financial Assistance. There are Institute of International education study abroad ranking universities take admission for our students without application fees. We offer majors in various filed like engineering, medicals, management, science , sports,films and many more.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Study Metro conduct word education fair in many metro cities, where will invite our abroad university delegates for spot admission for our indian students. We also help to get education loan for higher study from our various partner banks.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>If you list of Overseas Education Consultants in Bangalore and Indore will find Study Metro is Best Overseas Consultancy. We are Global Education Consultancy help Indian,Pakistan,Sri Lanka,Bangladesh, Nigeria, Ghana and African students to make their dream come true to Study Abroad.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Study Metro is Best Overseas Job Consultant, who will conduct Work and Study programs in Various countries like USA,Canada,France, Switzerland,Dubai and many more. Candidates can apply with experience and there are equal chance for fresher to get kind of jobs in abroad where salaries are more than 1 Lacks per month.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Education Abroad never been this much easy. With an experienced and dedicated team of counsellors, the firm has been successfully helping students get into top universities, for the past several years. Now tied up with schools that offer work programs for students, the firm ensures that students earn money while pursuing their respective course of study.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>We mainly deals with those universities Overseas universities that teach in English Language and provide affordable fees for international students. We also help students to booking cheap flights and forex for good conversation rate. We have dedicate Travel Disks Advisor to manager all these king of inquires.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Studying abroad and Overseas Degree expands a student''s experiences and personal growth by introducing them to new cultures, places and people. Future employers favour applicants that have international experiences as it proves they can easily adjust to changes and new configurations.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Study Metro made Education Abroad Essay and Affordable also with work and study programs, students does not have to depends on parents for fees and living expense. There are also Free education programs offered in Europe for MBA,MS,PhD and Bachelor programs. Read Abroad Articles for more information.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>There are so many advantages and benefits to study abroad, Student can get post-study work visa for 2-3 years. Studying at an international university does not cost any more than studying at an Indian college. While studying abroad, students are guaranteed a job and can begin working from Day 1.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Study Metro will get you the admission in World ranking universities and guide to to get scholarship/Grants if you have good score of IELTS/GRE/GMAIT/TOEFL. There are some college offer admission with these exam as well.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe style="border: 1px solid #CCC; border-width: 1px; margin-bottom: 5px; max-width: 100%;" src="//www.slideshare.net/slideshow/embed_code/key/vYUBnUYL3JbBmP" width="595" height="485" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"> </iframe></p>\r\n<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;"><strong> <a title="The Build Trap" href="//www.slideshare.net/MelissaPerri/the-build-trap-66849122" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Build Trap</a> </strong> from <strong><a href="//www.slideshare.net/MelissaPerri" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Melissa Perri</a></strong></div>', 2, 'About US', 'About US', 'About US', 1, '2016-08-29 13:17:26', 0, 'canberra_hero_image.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1),
(5, 'Home', 'home', '<h2><strong>Welcome to Study Metro</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Study Metro is a professional education consultancy firm, extending excellent support and service to students all over India and gives unlimited study opportunities across the Globe. Our aim is to improve educational standards. Scores of parents have sought our advice to find suitable Universities for their children.&nbsp;</p>', 1, 'Home', 'Home', 'Home', 1, '2016-08-29 13:19:17', 0, 'singapore_abroad.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1),
(6, 'University', 'university', '<p>The United States is recognized for the world class education and premiere destination for<a href="http://page.studymetro.com/Work-and-Study-USA"><strong>international students</strong></a>&nbsp;from all over the globe.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAmerican universities are widely known for the quality of their teaching and research. The United States is the number one and largest destination for international students seeking higher education overseas. The education system in USA is the most versatile and flexible higher education system for international students in the world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nToday about 30 percent of all current international students in the world are studying in the United States. Have you ever wondered what makes U.S. higher education so popular in the world?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNearly 600,000 students from all over the world came to the United States last year to study at both undergraduate and graduate levels. Without a doubt, America offers very high quality post secondary education. There are more than 4,000 public and private colleges, community colleges and universities in the USA, including over 600 public four-year colleges and universities and over 1,650 private four-year colleges and universities.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAmerican schools are the number 1 choice for international students and possess the greatest quantity of world rated colleges. Studying in the united states provides you with the opportunity to expand your job options, explore an enormous and various nation, and discover from worldwide-famous instructors and scientists at US schools and Graduate schools.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe option of colleges in the united states may be the biggest on the planet. A United States college is generally more compact while offering only undergraduate levels, while a college also provides graduate levels. In every US college or college you&#39;ll find schools (or ability) that specialize inside a area of interest like Business. Regardless of what where you need to study, there&#39;s a training course that&#39;s best for you.</p>\r\n', 3, 'University', 'University', 'University', 1, '2016-08-29 13:24:48', 1, 'dummy.mp4', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1),
