campuses in Sydney and Melbourne. The University operates The Hotel School Sydney and The Hotel School Melbourne in partnership with Mulpha Australia.\n\nSouthern Cross Universitywas ranked #401-500 in the Times Higher Education World University Rankings 2015-2016\nSouthern Cross University is a research intensive university and was evaluated at ''well above world standard'' in nine key areas in the Australian Research Council''s 2015 Excellence in Research Australia Report .\nSCU International ranked number one in Australia, for the third year running, for international student support in the International Student Barometer (ISB) survey 2015 .\nIndustry-relevant degrees with a strong practical component that enables students to generate and apply knowledge.', 'Southern Cross University is in a unique part of Australia where students can access some of the best surfing beaches and marine environments in the country. World Heritage rainforest areas and national parks are also regional attractions - perfect for bushwalking and camping experiences.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(18, 'Spencer College', 1940, 'Australia', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Spencer-College.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Spencer.jpg', 'Queensland', '5 Hubert Street, Wolloongabba,Queensland 4102,Australia', '', 'IELTS 6 / TOFEL 80', 'PRIVATE', '9000-10000 AUD', 'Certificate IV in Business                           Diploma of Business                                     Diploma of International Business  Diploma of Leadership and Management                                                      Diploma of Marketing CRICOS No:  Diploma of Project Management Advanced Diploma of Business CRICOS  Advanced Diploma of Leadership and Management                                                Advanced Diploma of Marketing Advanced Diploma of Project Management                                                              Hospitality Courses\nCertificate III in Patisserie\nCertificate III in Commercial Cookery\nCertificate IV in Commercial Cookery\nDiploma of Hospitality\nEnglish Courses\nCertificate I in EAL (Access)\nCertificate II in EAL (Access)\nCertificate III in EAL (Access)\nCertificate IV in EAL (Further Study)\n- See more at: http://www.spencercollege.net.au/index.php/courses#sthash.5I2FX0w7.dpuf', '', '', '', '', 'ON/OFF CAMPUS', '61 7 3217 3313', 'admission@studymetro.com', '$20 000/yr', 'spring/fall, summer', NULL, '100', 'http://spencercollege.edu.au/', '', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LEJGz8LplnM', '', '["","","","","","","","","",""]', NULL, 'Spence College', 'Our Brisbane campus is centrally located at Woolloongabba, an inner city suburb approximately 2 kilometres from the central business district of Brisbane, the capital city of Queensland. There is easy access to accommodation, restaurants, food outlets, shops, cricket and football stadium, learning facilities and the State library.\n\nOur Southport Campus is located in the commercial hub of the famous Gold Coast, just 80 kilometres south of Brisbane. Here students will enjoy the relaxed atmosphere of a premier tourist destination with easy access once again to accommodation, restaurants, food outlets, shops, sports stadium, learning facilities and library.\n\nBoth Campuses are easily accessible by public transport due to their prime locations.', 'As a nationally recognised RTO, Spencer College are fully committed to continuous improvement. Our uncompromising stance on ‚Äústudent integrity‚Äù has earned us the reputation that we currently enjoy. Spencer College takes pride in its ever expanding faculties of Business, Management, Tourism and Hospitality and are proud to offer our services to students from 10 different nationalities.\n\nSpencer College has excellent student support services. Our friendly staff values our students by ensuring their needs are met. Spencer College values its experienced and friendly staff.\n\nCourses are practical and functional, preparing individuals with a mix of well-rounded skills and knowledge to embark on an interesting career.\n\nSpencer College has grown every year since its inception and looks forward to future growth including higher education programs, a wider range of courses and the opening of new campuses.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
