(21, 'Taylors College', 1920, 'Australia', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Taylors-College.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Taylors-College.jpg', 'Waterloo', 'Lv 2 965 Bourke Street, Waterloo NSW 2017, Australia', '', 'IELTS 6 / TOFEL 80', 'PRIVATE', '9000-10000 AUD', 'Diploma of Science                                                   Diploma of Commerce', '', '', '', '', 'ON/OFF CAMPUS', '61 2 8303 9700', 'admission@studymetro.com', '$11,940 /yr', 'spring/fall, summer', NULL, '100', 'www.taylorscollege.edu.au/\n', 'http://www.taylorscollege.edu.au/about/connect', 'https://twitter.com/taylorscollege', '', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/taylors-college-australia\n', 'https://www.instagram.com/mytaylorscollege/\n', 'http://www.youtube.com/TaylorsCollegeAusNZ', '', '["","","","","","","","","",""]', NULL, 'Taylors College', 'WHY CHOOSE TAYLORS\n\nAt Taylors College, our unique learning environment allows you to fulfil your ambitions and to enjoy life at university and beyond.\n\nOur students‚Äô successes\n\nAny College should be measured against the results of their students. We are proud to be judged by the results and achievements of our students. Find out more>\n\nLocation, location, location\n\nTaylors College campuses are located in some of the best cities in the world. The advantage of studying in Australia or New Zealand is that you can enjoy the metropolitan city lifestyle while not being too far away from the stunning outdoor surrounds.', 'The best university preparation\n\nOur aim is to provide you with the best preparation to excel at University. Our curriculum is adapted and personalized to suit you and your needs.  We‚Äôll work with you to develop your complete skill base ‚Äì academic, linguistic, cultural and social ‚Äì so that you become a confident student who will succeed at University. Our courses cover English Language Preparation, High School programs, University Foundation programs and Diploma of Commerce. Find out more about our course>\n\nThe best support and care\n\nMuch of our early support involves helping you adapt to life in a new country.  Having helped thousands of students, we know what to expect and how to help. As you begin your studies, our care extends to providing you with a well-established network of people to advise and help you with any problems with your studies, health or career options. Each campus has a Student Welfare Officer who is available to assist with a variety or personal problems. Find out more>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
