niversity, student success is our priority. We empower our students to reach their goals with flexible learning options, individualized student services, hands-on learning opportunities, and a diverse, inclusive environment.\nFor 45 years TRU has taken pride in providing an excellent education to every student that comes to us‚Äîfrom a wide variety of backgrounds and perspectives, at various stages of the learning journey. Nearly 26,000 students study on our campuses in Kamloops and Williams Lake, or in distance or online courses and programs through Open Learning.\n', 'Why Thompson Rivers University?\nFrom traditional academics to trades, from certificates to graduate degrees, TRU offers over 140 on-campus programs and 60 Open Learning programs to choose from. Our students apply what they learn in co-op work terms, study abroad, undergraduate research, field schools and practicums, service learning and other opportunities‚Äîwith guidance and mentorship by our accessible faculty. Research, creation and innovation thrive in our open, flexible learning environment. And so do our students\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(52, 'University Canada West', 2005, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7420&action=edit', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7549&action=edit', ' Vancouver, Canada', '626 W Pender St #100, Vancouver, BC V6B 1V9, Canada', NULL, '6.5 IELTS score or better', 'Private', '$CAD 10,000 approx', ' Bachelor of Commerce r of Commerce\n Bachelor of Arts in Business Communication  \nMBA\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 800-288-9502', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ucanwest.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/UniversityCanadaWest/', 'https://twitter.com/ucanwest', 'https://plus.google.com/+UcanwestCa', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/university-canada-west-10805', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/256384739/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/CanadaUniversity', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'University Canada West', '\nUniversity Canada West is a contemporary independent university located in the heart of vibrant Vancouver. Established in 2004, UCW offers a range of career-focused programs including the Bachelor of Commerce, Bachelor of Arts in Business Communication and Master of Business Administration. Courses are offered at our downtown Vancouver campus. \n', 'University Canada West is a business-oriented, teaching-intensive university. We deliver programs that provide students with the applied and theoretical basis for success in the workplace and future academic endeavors.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(53, 'Vancouver International College', NULL, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7445&action=edit', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7551&action=edit', 'Vancouver, Canada', '549 Howe St 2nd Floor, Vancouver, BC V6C 2C2, Canada', NULL, 'IELTS TOEFL iBT TOEFL PBT TOEFL CBT CLB CEF\nAdvanced Band 5.5 - 6.0+ 80+ 550+ 215 - 230 Essay 4.0+ CLB10 C2\n', 'Private', '$CAD 10,000 approx', 'General ESL\nIntensive Speaking & Listening\nProfessional Speaking & Writing\nIELTS\nCollege Preparation\nSpeaking Clinic\nReal Canadian Pronunciation\nBusiness Communication\nCommunication Arts\nReal Canadian Pronunciation 2\nMedical English\nWriting\nTOEIC\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 604-893-8423', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://vicedu.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/VancouverInternationalCollege.VIC/', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/vancouver-international-college', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/6433420/', NULL, NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Vancouver International College ', 'Vancouver International College (VIC) is a well-established independent school, duly registered with the BC Ministry of Education.\nOur mission is to grant students a pathway to a university degree in Canada that will open doors to numerous opportunities for future success. VIC provides a solid foundation for advanced studies in the liberal arts and sciences by offering government-accredited UP courses and rigorous ESL training while maintaining high academic standards and giving careful attention to the individual needs of each student. ', 'We strive to create a supportive and inspiring environment for students in order to encourage them to pursue academic excellence, and to develop a life-long passion for learning. Our knowledgeable and committed staffs work tirelessly to ensure our students become responsible and compassionate world citizens who demonstrate innovation, leadership, commitment and integrity in all their endeavors.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(54, 'Alexander College', 2006, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7380&action=edit', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7450&action=edit', 'Burnaby, Canada', '4603 Kingsway #101, Burnaby, BC V5H 4M4, Canada', NULL, 'IBT TOEFL\n*Alexander College TOEFL Code: 3317 80 overall, and 19 in reading, 19 in writing, 18 in listening, 18 in speaking\nIELTS (Academic) 6.0 and writing > 6.0', 'Private', '$CAD 10,000 approx', '\nAssociate of Arts\nAssociate of Arts (Business)\nAssociate of Arts (Economics)\nAssociate of Arts (Psychology)\nAssociate of Science\nEnglish for Academic Purposes', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 604-435-5815', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://alexandercollege.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/AlexanderCollege', 'https://twitter.com/alexander_edu', 'https://plus.google.com/116654844472835355851', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alexander-college', 'https://www.instagram.com/alexandercollege/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/acbccanada', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Alexander College', 'Alexander College helps young people benefit from participating in the higher education community. We provide the first two years of university study leading to an Associate degree and university transfer in a student-centered and supportive environment.', 'Why Alexander College?\nHere are ten reasons why Alexander College may be a good choice for you:\n1. Well qualified, fully engaged staff and instructors available to provide student-centered support.\n2. Small class sizes, with limits set at 35 students or less for all subjects.\n3. Full transferable courses within the BC Transfer System to colleges and universities within BC.\n4. Personalized academic planning and advising services.\n5. Free tutoring for all courses.\n6. Individualized support in the Writing and Learning Centre.\n7. Consideration of international course work and credentials.\n8. An urban experience, with campuses located in central Burnaby and Vancouver.\n9. Inclusive and interactive clubs, events, and indoor/outdoor activities.\n10. Affordable fees compared with public colleges and universities.\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(55, 'Algoma University', 1967, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7424&action=edit', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7451&action=edit', 'Ontario, Canada', '1520 Queen St E, Sault Ste. Marie, Ontario, Canada', NULL, 'ENG4U, two U/M Math\n(Data Management recommended) Min Avg 65%', 'Public', '$CAD 11,000 approx', '\nAccounting\nAnishinaabemowin\nBiology\nBusiness Administration\nCommunity Development\nCommunity Economic and Social Development (CESD)\nComputer Science\nEconomics\nEnglish and Film\nFinance and Economics\nFine Arts\nFrench\nGeography and Geology\nHistory and Philosophy\nLaw and Justice\nMathematics\nMusic\nPolitical Science\nPsychology\nSocial Work\nSociology', 'Craig Chamberlin', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 705-949-2301', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.algomau.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/algomau/', 'https://twitter.com/AlgomaU', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/algoma-university', 'https://www.instagram.com/algomau/', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-xkRzdDme7uyBT0I9fFs3g', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Algoma University', 'Algoma University is a postsecondary institution in Sault Ste. Marie, Ontario, Canada, offering undergraduate university degrees in more than 30 academic programs. \n\n\nIn addition to the main campus, Algoma U offers distinct academic programming in two other locations in the province: Brampton and Timmins. These locations provide unique learning experiences in specific program areas tailored to the communities they serve. At Algoma University, no matter where you choose to study you will receive a personalized educational experience and one-on-one attention from faculty in a caring community of learners.\n\n', 'Why Algoma University ?\nAlgoma University‚Äôs unique learning experience provides students with greater opportunities. The personal attention that students receive from smaller class sizes and personalized instruction from professors who are experts in their chosen field gives Algoma U students a distinct advantage\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(56, 'Alpha International Academy', 2008, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7381&action=edit', NULL, ' Scarborough,, Canada', '3405 Kennedy Rd, Scarborough, ON M1V 4Y3, Canada', NULL, 'TOEFL 78        IELTS 6.5  PTE 55', 'Public', '$CAD 11,000 approx', 'http://www.slc-alpha.ca/programs/', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off campus', '1 416-640-0161', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.slc-alpha.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/alphainternationacademy/', 'https://twitter.com/slc_alpha', 'https://plus.google.com/105708378024850615748', 'https://in.linkedin.com/in/alpha-international-5702a64', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/235751855/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ec1t8C0LpG8', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Alpha International Academy', 'At St. Lawrence College @ Alpha we focus on providing our students with a healthy competitive learning environment. The quality of education is among the highest for community colleges in Ontario. This acts as a testimony to our ability to consistently exceed expectations. Our programs are designed to equip our students with excellent skills to cater the best opportunities in the industry. Our qualified and experienced staff ensures a smooth integration of graduates into the workforce.', 'Why Alpha International Academy    \n‚Ä¢ Students will graduate with a diploma from a public institution operating in accordance to the Ministry of Training Colleges and Universities in the Province of Ontario\n\n‚Ä¢ Students experience Toronto‚Äôs multicultural environment\n\n‚Ä¢ A three-year post-graduation work permit may be available to St. Lawrence College graduates\n\n‚Ä¢ Degree options available through articulation agreements with universities across Canada and USA\n\n‚Ä¢ High graduate employment rate\n\n‚Ä¢ Off-campus work permit possible\n\n‚Ä¢ Great work opportunities in Toronto\n\n‚Ä¢ Easy access to public transportation\n\n‚Ä¢ Fre