(76, 'Interlangues Language School', 1976, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7398&action=edit', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7497&action=edit', 'Ottawa,  Canada', '444 Maclaren, Ottawa, ON K2P 0M8, Canada', NULL, NULL, 'Private', '$CAD 10,000 approx', 'University/College Preparation\nInterlangues will fully prepare you for your post-secondary education. Whether it be Test Preparation, a particular skill focus, or subject specific vocabulary, we have the perfect program for you.\n\nInterlangues can help you prepare for all the major English tests such as:\nTOEFL\nTOEIC\nEAP (English for Academic Purposes)\nIELTS, etc.\n\nWe also offer focused training on particular language skills such as:\nPhonetics and Pronunciation\nAcademic Writing\nPublic Speaking\n\nInterlangues can prepare you for specific College or University Programs with our subject specific vocabulary programs such as:\nEnglish for Law\nEnglish for Engineering\nEnglish for Petroleum Engineering\nEnglish for International Communication\nBusiness English\nand many more.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '1 613-236-3764', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://interlangues.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/interlangues1976/', 'https://twitter.com/interlangues76', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Interlangues+Language+School/@45.4137385,-75.6997899,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x4cce05ada0167571:0x4ebe54f87fc59ba2!8m2!3d45.4137348!4d-75.6976012?hl=en_uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/interlangues-language-school', 'https://www.instagram.com/interlangues76/', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYtzGOOQxPKXiB9KjSfhLRQ', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Interlangues Language School', 'Interlangues was established in 1976 by Christiane Millet-Alexis, the current C.E.O., and has successfully trained thousands of Canadian and International students. The City of Ottawa, the Department of External Affairs