(93, 'Study Abroad Canada Language Institute', NULL, 'Canada', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7414&action=edit', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-admin/post.php?post=7539&action=edit', ' Charlottetown, Canada', '223 Queen St, Charlottetown, PE C1A 4B7, Canada', NULL, NULL, 'Private', '$CAD 10,000 approx', 'Intensive English Program\nJunior Vacation & Study Tours\nGroups\nPrivate Classes\nDistance Learning Program\nJunior/Senior High School Preparation\nUniversity Preparation Program\nTeacher Training Certificate', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/off Campus', ' 1 (902) 628-2379', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.studyincanada.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/studyabroadcanada/', 'https://twitter.com/studyabroadcan', 'https://plus.google.com/110994772789671723668', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/study-abroad-canada-language-institute', 'https://www.instagram.com/studyabroadcanada/', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCU0opf2nosJYybnZE8YA21A', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Study Abroad Canada Language Institute', 'As a world famous language school offering programs since 1994, SACLI is dedicated to the educational goals of students from around the world.   We have partnerships with some of the highest ranking universities in Canada, as well as both the provincial and federal governments. With our newly developed curriculum, you have the flexibility of following either a career or academic focused language training program. One of our friendly staff will always be ready to help you every step of the way.', 'Why Study Abroad Canada Language Institute?\nWe offer a variety of quality programs with small classes and excellent instruction. If your main focus is to improve your English, our Intensive English Program will help you reach your goal. Others choose one of our Study Tour programs which include morning classes and afternoon activities. Our friendly, qualified instructors will work with 