(102, 'Nanjing University of Aeronautics and Astronautics (NUAA)', 1952, 'China', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/NUAA_logo.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/NanJingNUAA_20121019-1024x575.jpg', ' Nanjing, Jiangsu, China', 'iangjun Alley, Xuanwu, Nanjing, Jiangsu, China', NULL, NULL, 'Public', NULL, 'http://iao.nuaa.edu.cn/find-a-course.html', 'Nie Hong (??)', '20619', NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', NULL, 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://iao.nuaa.edu.cn/', 'https://www.facebook.com/nuaa.official', 'https://twitter.com/nuaa_official', 'https://plus.google.com/s/Nanjing%20University%20of%20Aeronautics%20and%20Astronautics/top', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/nanjing-university-of-aeronautics-and-astronautics-11254', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/246361970/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GMRIc8br1k8', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Nanjing University of Aeronautics and Astronautics(NUAA)', 'Nanjing University of Aeronautics and Astronautics (NUAA) is one of China‚Äôs premier learning and research institutions which now develops into a comprehensive university especially featured with Aerospace Engineering. Ever since it was established in 1952, we have strived to conduct world-level research and education system. Nearly 60 years‚Äô history witnesses its unremitting efforts and remarkable achievements.', 'Academia and education at NUAA represent strong capacity among all the universities in China. It has acquired national status through the quality of its excellence research work, especially in the areas of Aerospace Engineering, Mechanics, Electromechanics, Economy and Management, etc.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(103, 'SBC', 2006, 'China', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/SBC.gif', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Sbc.png', ' Shanghai,China', '1195 Fuxing Zhong Road Shanghai 200031, PRC ,China', NULL, NULL, 'Private', NULL, 'English foundation year\n‚Äì Semester exchange program\n‚Äì China / UK Mixed Degree Programs\n‚Äì Bachelor‚Äôs in Manufacturing Systems Engineering\n‚Äì Bachelor‚Äôs in Industrial Electronics and Engineering\n‚Äì Bachelor‚Äôs in Event Management', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '86 (0)21 6431 9899', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.sbc-usst.edu.cn/en', 'https://www.facebook.com/SinoBritishCollege/', 'https://twitter.com/SBCShanghai', 'https://plus.google.com/112402442090648453837', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/735720?trk=tyah', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/user/InternationalSBC06', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'the sino british college usst china', 'The Sino-British College (SBC) is an international university college, jointly established by the University of Shanghai for Science & Technology (USST), and 9 leading British Universities: The University of Bradford, The University of Huddersfield, The University of Leeds, Leeds Beckett University, Liverpool John Moores University, Manchester Metropolitan University, The University of Salford, The University of Sheffield, and Sheffield Hallam University.', 'SBC became a fully licensed university college on September 1st, 2006. It is the only Shanghai-based higher education institution to be awarded a license by the Chinese Ministry of Education to offer full degree programmes taught entirely in English to multiple overseas universities (the so-called "1 to N Consortium Model"), either taught entirely at the Shanghai campus, or with a period of study abroad. Graduates are awarded degrees from one of the partner British institutions. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
