ompanies, the business world and civil society around 10 universal principles for labour and environmental standards and human rights. We were the first business school in France to join the Global Compact.\n\nSince then, we have been developing and disseminating our expertise in corporate social responsibility (CSR) and integrating it into our research, teaching and internal management.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
