t embodiment of the French way of life.\nVichy also boasts state-of-the-art sporting facilities situated in splendid natural surroundings.', 'A centre of excellence\nCAVILAM (Centre d‚ÄôApproches Vivantes des Langues et des M√©dias) was established in 1964 by the municipality of Vichy and the universities of Clermont-Ferrand. It joined the international Alliance fran√ßaise network in 2012.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(107, 'ECE Paris', 1919, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ECE.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ECE-Paris.jpg', 'Paris, France', '37 Quai de Grenelle, 75015 Paris, France', NULL, 'An International Bachelor‚Äôs degree (3 or 4 years) in science or technology (Bachelor of Science or Bachelor of Engineering).\nAll courses have English and/or French requirements. You must provide a proof of the language ability.\nEnglish language tests for all majors\n-IELTS: 6.0 (minimum) OR\n-TOEFL: 83 (iBT)\n-TOEIC: 780\nFrench language tests for majors offered in French\n-B2 level in any of the following tests: TCF, TEF, DELF or DALF   ', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'ENERGY & ENVIRONMENT  QUANTITATIVE FINANCE  HEALTH & TECHNOLOGY  INFORMATION SYSTEMS EMBEDDED SYSTEMS  CONNECTED THINGS  TRANSPORTATION & MOBILITY', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33184140302', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'September', 'http://www.ece.fr/school-of-engineering/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ECE.Paris/', 'https://twitter.com/ingenieursece?lang=en', 'https://plus.google.com/101882693187144496156', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/ece-paris-12304', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/280485025/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/IngenieursECE', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ece paris ', 'ECE Paris educates general and high-tech engineers eager to create solutions to today‚Äôs most pressing social challenges.\nDuring their studies in France and abroad, ECE Paris students gain the expertise required in all the major sectors: industry, manufacturing, energy, construction, transportation, trade and distribution, finance, insurance, administration, health, education, culture, media, etc.', '10 GOOD REASONS TO ENROLL AT ECE PARIS\n1. A master‚Äôs degree in Engineering recognized and accredited by the French Ministry of Higher Education and Research and the Council of Engineers.\n2. An engineering