ter in Mgt (specialisation in finance,marketing,consulting) 18000 per year\nMsc in Luxury Mgt & Mark', '120 Euro', NULL, 'September', 'http://www.em-lyon.com/en#', 'https://fr-fr.facebook.com/EMLYONBusinessSchool', 'https://twitter.com/EMLYON', 'https://plus.google.com/+emlyon', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/emlyon-business-school', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/2466417/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/EMLYON', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'emlyon business school ', 'Since its creation, emlyon business school has been driven by entrepreneurship, innovation and humanism. Our vision and mission are nurtured by our global and digital world. The entrepreneur from emlyon business school is a maker and an early mover. He is an early maker.', 'emlyon business school is a major force in the world of European Business Schools. We are one of the few business schools to hold triple accreditation from Equis, AACSB and AMBA.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(110, 'EPITA', 1984, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/EPITA.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Epit.jpg', ' Kremlin Bic√™tre Cedex, France', '14/16 Rue Voltaire, 94276 Kremlin Bic√™tre Cedex, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Master of Computer Engineering (ME) Master of Computer Science (MSc)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33144080101\n', 'admission@studymetro.com', '12400 Euro', '60 Euro', NULL, 'March & September', 'https://www.facebook.com/EPITA.International.Master', 'https://twitter.com/WorldEPITA', 'https://plus.google.com/+epita', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/school?id=20389', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/epita/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/EpitaOfficiel', NULL, NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'EPITA', 'Founded in 1984, EPITA is a renowned bilingual Graduate School of Computer Engineering situated in Paris. It is a member of IONIS Education Group, the leading private higher education group, with some 20 schools and educational institutions. Thanks to its unique pedagogical approach, EPITA trains its students to become outstanding engineers who boast a solid base of scientific knowledge and the most advanced skills in the digital sector.', 'A computer engineer trained at EPITA has a complete professional profile: as computer technology is omnipresent in all areas of a company, a digital engineer may work in the field of human resources, marketing, communication and even finance. EPITA is ranked among the five top computer engineering schools in France and has developed partnerships with a wide range of companies.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(111, 'ESC RENNES', 1990, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ESC_Rennes.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Esc.jpg', ' Rennes, France', '2 Rue Robert d''Arbrissel, 35065 Rennes, France', NULL, 'IELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Master in Management\nInternational Masters\nExecutive MBA\nBachelor in Management (IBPM)\nBachelor ESLI ¬ª\nExchange students\nDoctoral Programmes ¬ª\nSummer programme', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33299546363', 'admission@studymetro.com', '13000 Euro', NULL, NULL, 'September', 'https://www.esc-rennes.fr/', 'https://www.facebook.com/escrennes/', 'https://twitter.com/escrennes', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/esc-rennes', 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/locations/235211625/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ESCRennes', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ESC RENNES', 'The world has become a ‚Äúglobal village‚Äù where economies are closely interrelated, political, social and cultural dimensions tightly interwoven or openly confrontational. This brings considerable opportunities but also greater complexity. One ‚Äúmust prepare for the future by seeing what others cannot (‚Ä¶and) have others follow your direction when there is no map‚Äù.(1)', 'Management Schools have to face these new challenges, responding to companies needs, by educating and training students and managers to be the ‚ÄúResponsible Business Entrepreneurs‚Äù for tomorrow‚Äôs world.\n \nFor Rennes School of Business, it has led to the development of two main priorities: Internationalisation and Innovation.\nThe school intends to prepare Global Responsible Pionneers.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
