(121, 'TOULOUSE', 1903, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/TBS.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Toulouse-group-at-graduate-school-2014.jpg', 'Toulouse, France', '¬†20 Boulevard Lascrosses, 31068 Toulouse, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Bachelor in Management Program\nMaster of Business Administration (MBA)\nDoctorate of Business Administration (DBA)\nMaster in Management Program\n\nMSc. Banking & International Finance\nMSc. Supply Chain And Lean managEment (SCALE)\nSM2 Cluster\nMSc. Marketing, Management & Communication\nMSc. Sports, Marketing & Management\nMSc. Hospitality & Tourism Marketing & Management\nMSc. Digital Intelligence & Marketing Analytics (DIMA)\nMSc. Finance Barcelona\nMSc. Marketing Barcelona\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33561294949', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Bachelors In Management 7200 Euros p.a\nBachelors In Finance 7200 Euros p.a\nBachelors In Business 7200 Euros p.a\nBachelors In Marketing 7200 Euros p.a\n', '100 Euro', NULL, 'September', 'http://www.tbs-education.fr/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ToulouseBusinessSchool', 'https://twitter.com/ToulouseBS', 'https://plus.google.com/+tbs-education-fr', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/toulouse-business-school', 'https://www.instagram.com/toulousebs/', 'https://www.youtube.com/toulousebs', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'TOULOUSE', 'Three Campuses, Three Accreditations, One School Open to the World\nProfessionals today have to keep pace with the demands of a fast-changing business world. Toulouse Business School (TBS) is dedicated to providing its students with the analytical skills, professional network and agility needed to adapt, innovate, and anticipate change. As part of an economic, cultural, and educational center at the heart of Europe, our students have the knowledge and network to succeed wherever their career takes them.\n\nThrough a broad core curriculum and multiple specialization areas, business education at TBS builds practical skills for the business world of today ‚Äì and tomorrow. Discover TBS and its multilingual, multicultural, and interdisciplinary environment:', 'Specialized Business Education ‚Äì At the core of TBS is our wide range of undergraduate and graduate degree programs. We offer programs taught in French, English, or Spanish in the fields of Management, Business, Marketing, Finance, and Aerospace Management. We also offer elite Executive Education and specialized programs.  TBS also functions as a thriving center for business research. \nGlobal Network ‚Äì With 75 nationalities represented on our three campuses in Toulouse, Barcelona, and Casablanca, and two sites developing in Paris and London, as well as 160 Partner Universities worldwide, TBS is a global institution with a welcoming environment for international students.\nQuality Assurance and Rankings ‚Äì TBS offers internationally recognized degrees and is part of the prestigious 1% of business schools with the ‚Äútriple crown‚Äù of accreditations: EQUIS, AACSB, and AMBA. TBS ranks among the top business schools in France, and our Master in Management program is among Europe‚Äôs Top 20 (Financial Times, 2012 (link is external)).\nDynamic Corporate Relations ‚Äì Our distinguished research faculty features a teaching staff of 1,200 high-level professionals with diverse experience in business sectors. In addition, students in Toulouse can take advantage of our institutional connections to over one hundred multinational corporations including Airbus Group, Alcatel Space, Motorola, Siemens, and Sony.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(122, 'VATEL ', 1981, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1427113286logo_vatel_school_0.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Vatel.jpg', ' N√Æmes, France', '140 Rue Vatel, 30900 N√Æmes, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Bachelor Vatel\nInternational Hotel Management\nMBA Vatel\nInternational Hotel Management', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33466625706', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Bachelors in International Hotel Management 11,800 euros per year\nMasters in International Hotel Management  \nFoundation course(for those who are from', '330 Euro', NULL, 'March & September', 'http://www.vatel.fr/en', 'https://www.facebook.com/vatelschool', 'https://twitter.com/vatelschool', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/school?id=356046', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ecolehotelierevatel', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'VATEL ', 'Vatel trains operational managers and senior executives in the International Hotel and Tourism Management industries.\n\nWith 35 years of experience, our campuses located throughout the world convey the same internationally targeted courses to 7,000 students based on the tried and tested mixture of theoretical university courses followed by professional experience. ', 'This concept has a provable track record: our 29,000 alumni work in the most beautiful hotels on earth and 80% of them work in the hotel and tourist management fields. Their jobs include, amongst others, functions of General Manager of a hotel chain or individual hotel, Hotel Manager, Sales Manager, Marketing, Human Resources or Financial Management, Public Relations or Special Events Manager, Auditor, Housekeeper, Front Desk Manager, just to name a few. As for the other 20%, they are recruited in other fields, especially in luxury brand management, where decision-makers are convinced by their skills and know-how.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(123, 'ESAIP', 1987, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/esaip_angers4.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/esaip_angers4.jpg', 'Saint-Barth√©lemy-d''Anjou, France', '18 Rue du 8 Mai 1945, 49124 Saint-Barth√©lemy-d''Anjou, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'PROGRAMMES\nENGINEERING PROGRAMMES\nDigital Engineering ‚Äì Computer Science & Networks\nRisk, Health, Safety and Environmental Management\n BSC. & MSC. PROGRAMMES\nBachelor International Data Manager\nMSS Security Science\nM.Sc Digital Engineering & Big Data\n SHORT PROGRAMMES\nERASMUS Mobility\nSummer or Winter Programmes', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33241966510', 'admission@studymetro.com', '5550 Euro ', NULL, NULL, 'March & September', 'https://www.esaip.org/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/groupeesaip', 'https://twitter.com/groupeesaip', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/user/MaChaineESAIP', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ESAIP', '"The goal of the esaip group since 1989 has been to train men and women for the jobs of the future, in order for them to evolve at an international level and gain strong adaptation capabilities for the world of business. The know-how ¬´ Made in esaip ¬ª has proved itself throughout the years, most notably through international openings and the individual follow-up provided to every student\nand trainee. Founded on Lasallian values of accessibility for all to higher education, the mission of the esaip group is to help each of our students and trainees to achieve their goals.\nWe take up this daring challenge every year with success."', 'ESAIP is a Graduate school of Engineering proposing a generalist, broad-based 3 years course, starting at a Bac+2 level or based 5 years course, starting at a Bac level. ESAIP offers two Diplomas at Angers and Grasse:\n‚Ä¢ Computer science and networks\n‚Ä¢ Safety, environment and industrial risk managment.\n\nThe graduate school of Engineering is authorized by the ‚ÄúCommission des Titres d‚ÄôIng√©nieurs‚Äù, EUR-ACE label, member of the ‚ÄúConf√©rence des Grandes Ecoles‚Äù.\n\n ', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
