(128, 'ESC Clermont', 1919, 'France', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/esc_clermont.gif', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/esc-clermont.jpg', 'Clermont-Ferrand, France', '4 Boulevard Trudaine, 63000 Clermont-Ferrand, France', NULL, 'TOEFL IBT 80-TOEFL PBT 550- TOEIC 750\nIELTS 6.5-7.0(With band score no less than 6.0)', 'Private', '7,000 Euro', 'Bachelor program\nBachelor in International Management\n \nMaster in Management\nMaster in Management (Grand Ecole Program)\n \nMaster of Science\nMSc Control, Audit & Corporate Finance\nMSc International Business Development\nMSc International Project Management', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '33473982424', 'admission@studymetro.com', 'Msc in International Business Development 11000 euros\nMsc in International Project Management 11000 euros\nMsc in Finance & Auditing 11000 euros\nMaster', '175 Euro', NULL, 'September', 'http://www.esc-clermont.fr/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/escclermont', 'https://twitter.com/escclermont', 'https://plus.google.com/100043044165476380960?cfem=1', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/esc-graduate-school-of-management', 'https://www.instagram.com/esc_clermont/', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCPzI8GzEW52PI9MXYTx2_mw', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'ESC Clermont', 'The Ecole Sup√©rieure de Commerce de Clermont has made a solid place for itself since its creation in 1919. Under the patronage of the Ministry of Commerce, the city of Clermont-Ferrand, the Conseil G√©n√©ral du Puy-de-D√¥me (General Council), the Chamber of Commerce and several companies in partnership with the General Council, the ESC Clermont welcomed a first class of 76 students. Since then, more than 11 000 men and women from all walks of life have trodden the grounds of the Trudaine campus.', 'To train lucid and responsible managers, entrepreneurs and leaders :\n\n‚Ä¢ Possessing fundemental knowledge in Management.\n\n‚Ä¢ Capable of understanding the complexity and the stakes of the economic and business environment where creativity and innovation are keys to successful decision making, and successful actions.\n\n‚Ä¢ Who create value on the economic, social and business fronts.\n\nWe accompany our students towards professional excellence using efficient and original methods.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
