(212, 'Liverpool John Moores University', 1823, 'UK', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/john-moores.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/john-moores1.jpg', ' Liverpool, United Kingdom', '70 Mount Pleasant, Liverpool L3 5UA, United Kingdom', NULL, 'IELTS\n6.0 (Min 5.5 in each component)\n\nPearson\n50-57\n\n', 'Public', '¬£10,000', 'https://www.ljmu.ac.uk/study/courses', NULL, '20,365', NULL, NULL, 'On Campus /Off Campus', '44 151 231 2121', 'admission@studymetro.com', '¬£12,360', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.ljmu.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/liverpooljohnmooresuniversity', 'https://twitter.com/LJMU', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/liverpool-john-moores-university-12607', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/user/LJMUTV', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Liverpool John Moores University', 'In 1823 a small institution was founded that was to revolutionise education in Liverpool and provide opportunities for the working people of the city.\nThe Liverpool Mechanics Institute was founded by people of power and influence who recognised the transformative effects of education and the impact that learning and aspiration could have on individuals, communities and society.  It was the first such institution to be founded in England.  \n\nThis small, pioneering movement was followed by the establishment of the Liverpool Institute and School of Art and the Liverpool Nautical College, and in 1900 Irene Mabel Marsh opened the IM Marsh campus. These organisations together laid the foundations for Liverpool John Moores University, an institution that has grown and flourished and continues to provide opportunities for all.', 'One University\nWe are an ambitious and forward thinking institution that challenges convention and believes passionately in the concept of ‚ÄòOne University‚Äô ‚Äì a community working together to achieve common student-centered objectives within a clear strategy.\nOur Vision\nTo be recognised as a modern civic university delivering solutions to the challenges of the 21st century.\n\nOur Mission\nCreating a community for learning and knowledge\n\nOur mission is to create and sustain a vibrant community for learning and knowledge where staff and students work together in an active and supportive partnership; providing opportunities to enrich our students, partners and the wider society through education, training, research, scholarship and knowledge transfer.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(213, 'LONDON COLLEGE OF INTERNATIONAL BUSINESS STUDIES', NULL, 'UK', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/London-College-Of-business-studies.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/London-College-Of-business-studies1.jpg', 'London , United Kingdom', 'Dock Offices, Surrey Quays Rd, London SE16 2XU, United Kingdom', NULL, 'IELTS\n6.0 (Min 5.5 in each component)', 'Public', '¬£10,000', 'Certificate in Strategic Management and Leadership\nExtended Diploma in Strategic Management & Leadership\nMBA Top-Up\nBBA Top-Up\n\nHND Diploma in Business (Management)\nHND Diploma in Business (Marketing)\nHND Diploma in Business (Human Resources)\nHND Diploma in Business (Accounting)\nHND Diploma in Business (Public Relations)\nHND Diploma in Business (Hospitality)\nHND Diploma in Business (Travel & Tourism)\nHND Diploma in Business (Sport & Leisure Management)\n\n\n\nHNC Certificate in Business (Management)\nHNC Certificate in Business (Marketing)\nHNC Certificate in Business (Human Resources)\nHNC Certificate in Business (Accounting)\nHNC Certificate in Business (Public Relations)\nHNC Certificate in Business (Hospitality)\nHNC Certificate in Business (Travel & Tourism)\nHNC Certificate in Business (Sport & Leisure Management)\n\n\nCertificate/Diploma in Business Administration\nCertificate/Diploma in Management\nCertificate/Diploma in Marketing\nCertificate/Diploma in Human Resources\nCertificate/Diploma in Accounting\nCertificate/Diploma in Public Relations\nCertificate/Diploma in Hospitality\nCertificate/Diploma in Travel & Tourism\nCertificate/Diploma in Sport & Leisure Management\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus /Off Campus', NULL, 'admission@studymetro.com', '¬£7,550 or ¬£9,000 (including Internship)', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.lcibs.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/LCIBS', 'https://twitter.com/LCIBS', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/london-college-of-international-business-studies', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3Ewv