(214, 'London School of Business and Management', NULL, 'UK', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/london-school-of-business-and-management-logo.jpg', 'About the University\nThe University of Sussex is a leading higher education and research institution near Brighton, in the south of England. Sussex was the first of the new wave of UK universities founded in the 1960s, receiving its Royal Charter in ', ' London, United Kingdom', 'Dilke House, 1 Malet St, London WC1E 7JN, United Kingdom', NULL, 'Undergraduate ‚Äì IELTS 6.0 overall, with all components 5.5 or above\nMBA and MSc Management ‚Äì IELTS 6.5 overall, with all components 5.5 or above\nLLM ‚Äì IELTS 6.5 overall, with all components 6.0 or above\n', 'Public', '¬£10,000', 'Undergraduate Courses\nBusiness\nLaw\nAccounting\nPostgraduate Courses\nBusiness\nLaw', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus /Off Campus', '44 20 7078 8840', 'admission@studymetro.com', '¬£10,000 ', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.lsbm.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/1LSBM/', 'https://twitter.com/lsbm', 'http://uk.linkedin.com/company/london-school-of-business-and-management', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/user/LondonBusinessSchool', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'London School of Business and Management', 'The London School of Business and Management is a vibrant and contemporary learning community that seeks to meet the needs of all our students by offering networking opportunities and a uniquely international environment. We are proud of our diverse and vibrant student body.\n', 'We offer a range of valuable services to accommodate the needs of our students and to help them adjust to London‚Äôs rich and diverse way of life, including:\nan excellent location in the heart of London‚Äôs academic area of Bloomsbury, full of vibrant student life and close to numerous libraries, museums and centres of research, not to mention our proximity to the hub of business and finance that is the City of London.\na very welcoming environment of inclusivity and diversity\nhighly competitive fees; amongst the best value provision in the UK\ntransferability of credit accumulated on other courses undertaken at selected educational institutions within the UK and around the world\nopportunities to gain valuable professional experience through the work placement module on both undergraduate and postgraduate courses\nhelp and support with visa applications for non-EU students\nhelp and support in finding suitable and affordable accommodation\nextra English language support classes if required\nthe services of our faculty members, many of whom hold a PhD or are working towards their doctorate ‚Äì our lecturers also have practice-based experience, providing our students with a ‚Äòreal-world‚Äô dimension to their academic studies\nsmall class sizes allowing lecturers to provide excellent individual support in a collaborative learning context', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(215, 'Met Film School', 2003, 'UK', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/MET_FILM_WHTE.jpg', 'https://www.instagram.com/sussexuni/', ' London, United Kingdom', 'Bldg E Ealing Studios, Ealing Green, London W5 5EP, United Kingdom', NULL, 'IELTS\n6.0 (Min 5.5 in each component)', 'Public', '¬£10,000', '2-YEAR DEGREE\nBA (HONS) PRACTICAL FILMMAKING\n3-YEAR DEGREE\nBA (HONS) PRACTICAL FILMMAKING\nDIPLOMA OF HIGHER EDUCATION\nPRACTICAL FILMMAKING DIPLOMA (DIP HE)\nCERTIFICATE OF HIGHER EDUCATION\nCERTIFICATE IN PRACTICAL FILMMAKING COURSE\nMA\nDIRECTING\nMA\nPRODUCING\nMA\nCINEMATOGRAPHY\nMA\nSCREENWRITING\nMA\nPOSTPRODUCTION\nMA\nDOCUMENTARY & FACTUALSIX-MONTH\nPRACTICAL FILMMAKING\nSIX-MONTH\nPOSTPRODUCTION\nSIX-MONTH\nDIGITAL ANIMATION & VFX  FILMMAKING\nFROM STORY TO SCREEN IN EIGHT WEEKS\nDOCUMENTARY\nDOCUMENTARY FILMMAKING\nFILMMAKING\nFOUR-WEEK FILMMAKING\nEDITING & POSTPRODUCTION\nTHREE-WEEK EDITING\nACTING\nACTING FOR FILM LEVEL 1\nACTING\nACTING FOR FILM LEVEL 2\nCINEMATOGRAPHY\nINTRODUCTION TO CINEMATOGRAPHY\nPOSTPRODUCTION\nSIX-MONTH DIGITAL ANIMATION & VFX\nFILMMAKING\nSIX-MONTH PRACTICAL FILMMAKING\nPOSTPRODUCTION\nSIX-MONTH POSTPRODUCTION', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus /Off Campus', NULL, 'admission@studymetro.com', '¬£17,500', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/MetFilmSchool', 'https://twitter.com/MetFilmSchool', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/met-film-school?trk=ppro_cprof', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/c/metfilmschool', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Met Film School', 'Review by the Quality Assurance Agency for Higher Education\n\nFrom the evidence provided in the annual return and at the monitoring visit, the review team concluded that Met Film School has made commendable progress with implementing the action plan from the September 2014:\n\nThe School continues to operate as one of three interconnected businesses, along with a commercial film production company and a post-production company, both of which provide opportunities for work placements and graduate employment. It continues to develop its curriculum further by promoting and expanding current industry links and expertise, and award-winning industry professionals continue to teach on the programmes.\nThe School continues to provide and expand the variety of employment opportunities for students and to monitor graduate employment statistics. Met Film School Graduate Opportunities (Met GO) is now firmly embedded within the School‚Äôs ethos.\nThe School continues to enhance its rigorous approach to admissions and the innovative induction process.', 'The BA (Hons) Practical Filmmaking Programme has been awarded a Creative Skillset Tick. This award is a mark of quality indicating programmes best suited to prepare students for a career in the creative industries.\nTo gain the Creative Skillset Tick, programmes need to undergo a rigorous assessment process conducted by experts in the creative industries. They only give the Tick to programmes with the strongest links with industry. This ensures that the courses keep up the rapid pace of creative change, and students‚Äô benefit from using the latest technologies an working with industry throughout their studies.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
