ry has made Royal Holloway the world-leading university it is today. These farsighted Victorians not only left us our extraordinary Founder‚Äôs Building (modelled on a French Ch√¢teau) and a history of academic ‚Äòfirsts‚Äô; their spirit also lives on in our values and culture ‚Äì to inspire individuals to succeed while maintaining our community spirit.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(221, 'Sheffield Hallam University', 1969, 'UK', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Sheffield_Hallam_University_logo.svg_.png', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/university-of-surrey', ' Sheffield  United Kingdom', 'Howard St, Sheffield S1 1WB, United Kingdom', NULL, 'IELTS 6.5 overall, with all components 6.0 or above', 'Public', '¬£10,000', 'https://www.shu.ac.uk/study-here/find-a-course', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus /Off Campus', '44 (0)114 225 5555', 'admission@studymetro.com', '¬£', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.shu.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/sheffieldhallamuniversity', 'https://twitter.com/sheffhallamuni', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.instagram.com/sheffhallamuni/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/sheffieldhallamuni', NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Sheffield Hallam University', 'Facilities\nThe Facilities Directorate provides the range of essential services which underpin the unique Sheffield Hallam University experience and add value to university life.\nEvents\nWe have access to a range of modern, extremely well-equipped meeting rooms and spaces. But there are other benefits to holding your event with us.\nEating\nThere are places to eat and drink in almost every building on campus, providing quality food and drink at competitive prices.\nThe Print Shop\nYour one-stop shop for all your printing needs. Whether you''re a student, a member of staff, or just someone who wants something printed well, quickly and efficiently. ', 'Study and career guidance\nBusiness start-up services\nOur business start-up services are available to all current students and alumni up to five years after graduation.\nCareers and employment\nOffers careers advice, guidance and information to enable our students and graduates to make well-informed decisions about their current and future plans.\nIT services\nWe have extensive IT facilities and offer expert support and advice to help you get the most out of our services.\nLibraries\nOur learning centres contain our library and information resources, including books, journals, DVDs, PCs, printers, photocopier, individual and group study spaces, and helpdesks to answer your queries.\nnetWORK\nFinding part-time and vacation work for current Sheffield Hallam students.\nStudent and Learning Services (SLS)\nA one-stop-shop for student advice and guidance services, also providing a range of learning and IT support for both staff and students.\nResearch and Innovation Office\nA contact point for business enquiries with a rapid, business-friendly response.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
