deis IBS offers bachelor‚Äôs, master‚Äôs and doctoral programs in business, finance and economics and has over 2,000 alumni serving in over 75 firms across 92 countries. Academics at Brandeis IBS focus on themes of international business and global economics, supplemented by over 60 faculty members, all of whom have research or corporate experience. Peter A. Petri was the founding dean at Brandeis IBS. More recently, Bruce R. Magid, Ph.D., has been appointed dean of the school, effective July 1, 2007.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(256, 'Bridge language Education', NULL, 'USA', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Bridge-Education-Group-Logo.png', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Bridge-Education-Group.jpg', 'Denver, CO ', '600 S Cherry St Suite520,Denver, CO 80246', NULL, NULL, 'Private', '$10,000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '303-777-7783', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, '$50', NULL, 'Spring / Summer / Fall', 'http://www.bridge.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/BridgeEducationGroup/', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'Bridge language Education', 'When you step through the doors of our language center, you become part of the Bridge family. Every year we host thousands of students from around the world, delivering top-notch language instruction, teacher training, and translation services.\nOur 80 full-time employees and 350 teachers form a diverse group of nationalities and cultures, and they understand the importance of language learning and cultural competency.\n', 'Our purpose challenges and unifies us in a common cause. At the very beginning of our 25 year history, we pioneered the use of video-laser discs in the language classroom as a teacher support system, and we have been at the forefront of innovation in the language industry ever since. We look forward to continuing this legacy far into the future.\nOur core values reflect the principles that guide us internally as an organization and with our customers. It is the essence of what we stand for\nOur Mission:\n‚ÄúTo transform lives and organizations by delivering excellence in language and education abroad.‚Äù\n\nOur Purpose:\n‚ÄúTo be the innovative leader in fostering effective communication and understanding across cultures \nworldwide.‚Äù\n\nOur Values:\nExcellence | Integrity | Learning Innovation | Teamwork\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
