t population that provide for various and extended learning opportunities for all. Not only does Castleton influence its students, but the students also have the ability and often do impact Castleton.\n\n‚ÄúCome to our campus, and you will learn that you too can make a difference in your university as you prepare to make a difference in the world.‚Äù  - President Dave Wolk\n\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(273, 'CHADRON STATE COLLEGE', 1911, 'USA', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Chadran-state.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Chadran-state1.jpg', 'Chadron, United States', '1000 Main St, Chadron, NE 69337, United States', NULL, 'Entrance requirements for the MBA based program\n.Complete application - the form is available at https://www.csc.edu/apply/now/\n.Earned baccalaureate degree from a regionally accredited institution with a grade point average of 2.75 or better on a 4.00 scale\n.Official transcripts from the college/university which issued bachelor''s degree. \n.Official transcripts from any institutions attended after receiving bachelor''s degree (if applicable)\n.New applicants will be required to complete the Inbound Peregrine Exam (Pre-Program Assessment). Students interested in obtaining an MBA degree are highly encouraged to complete the Inbound Peregrine Exam PRIOR to the starting of classes but it MUST be completed within the first two weeks. MBA students who do not successfully complete the Inbound Peregrine Exam by the end of the first course(s) are converted to a non-degree seeking status. This exam costs approximately $32.00, does not require any preparation, and takes approximately 2 hours to complete. A link and password to access the exam will be provided once the admission application has been processed. ?Students who attain a satisfactory score can then proceed with their MBA degree with no additional preparatory or prerequisite coursework needed.\n?Students who do not meet the minimum score established by the department on the Inbound Peregrine Exam will be required to take the Academic Leveling Course (ALC) through Peregrine Academic Services. The ALC course is comprised of fifteen modules and must be completed prior to enrollment of the next course. MBA students who do not successfully complete the ALC modules by the end of the first course(s) are converted to a non-degree seeking status. This self-paced course is designed to be a primer for the returning business major who has been out of school for a period of time. \n', 'Private', '$10,000', 'Master of Arts in Education (MAE)\nClinical Mental Health Counseling - partially online\nHistory - fully online\nScience and Mathematics\nScience - partially online\nMathematics - fully online\nMaster of Business Administration (MBA) - fully online\nMaster of Education (ME)\nCurriculum and Instruction - fully online\nGeneral Education (elementary)\nCareer and Technical Education (secondary)\nEducation Technology (elementary and secondary)\nMathematics (elementary and secondary)\nPhysical Education (elementary and secondary)\nReading Specialist PK-12\nSocial Science (elementary and secondary)\nSpecial Education K-12\nBusiness Education (secondary)\nCurriculum and Instruction - partially online\nLanguage Arts (elementary)\nScience (elementary and secondary)\nEducational Administration - fully online\nPrincipalship - Elementary, Secondary, Middle School or PK-12\nSpecial Education Supervisor Birth-12th grade\nCurriculum/Assessment Supervisor PK-12\nSchool Counseling - partially online\nMaster of Science in Organizational Management (MSOM)\nHuman Services - fully online\nSports Management - fully online\nNatural Resources - partially online', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '1 308-432-6000', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, '$50', NULL, 'Spring / Summer / Fall', 'http://www.csc.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/chadronstatecollege/', 'https://twitter.com/chadronstate', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/user/chadronstatecollege', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/chadronstatecollege', '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'CHADRON STATE COLLEGE', '\nChadron State College is located in Charon, Nebraska, has a population of approximately 6,000 residents. Chadron State, founded in 1885, is a public university located just one hour from one of of America''s most famous landmarks, Mount Rushmore. \n', 'The university enrolls some 3,000 students and offers some 80 Undergraduate and Graduate degree programs. The costs at Charon State are some of the lowest in the US. for 2015/2016 Undergraduate Tuition is just $2,600 per semester and Graduate Tuition is $4,000 per semester.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
