e to the world''s largest single-site collection of Frank Lloyd Wright architecture.\n\nThe 100-acre campus is a busy and active place where students are engaged in learning about the world while also living life to the fullest. FS students experience their education in classrooms, on campus, and through volunteer and intern experiences that take place with companies and organizations around the world. \n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
