 Letters and Sciences; the School of Business and Management; the School of Education; the School of Engineering and Computing; the School of Health and Human Services; and the School of Professional Studies. National University‚Äôs online academic programs are interactive with streaming videos, real-time discussions, multimedia learning material, and online classrooms.\nPrograms at National University are concentrated for adult learners and on-campus classes are scheduled during evenings and on weekends.\n\nAccreditation \nSince 1977, National University has been accredited by the Accrediting Commission for Senior Colleges and Universities of the Western Association of Schools and Colleges (WASC).\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
