(369, 'NEW YORK UNIVERSITY - SPS', NULL, 'USA', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NYU-Sps_long_color.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NYU-Sps.jpg', ' New York, NY, United States', '11 W 42nd St, New York, NY 10036, United States', NULL, 'Entrance Requirements- Graduates- Deadline for Fall 2016 was April 15, 2016\n- Application For Admission: Complete online \n- Application Fee - Is Waived- Contact CSUS to complete the waiver.\n- Official Transcripts- All Bachelors Transcripts (Minimum 3.0 on a 4.0 scale)\n- TOEFL (80) or IELTS (6.0) \n- ALI Evaluation Required- All student take an online English evaluation.\n- GMAT not needed for Business Program\n- GRE not needed for all other programs \n- Statement of Purpose\n- Resume\n- (2) Letters of Recommendation\n- Copy of Passport\n', 'Private', '$10,000', 'Construction Management   ‚Ä¢ \nDigital Applications, Advanced   ‚Ä¢ \nFundraising and Grantmaking   ‚Ä¢ \nGlobal Affairs   ‚Ä¢ \nHospitality Industry Studies   ‚Ä¢ \nHuman Resource Management   ‚Ä¢ \nHuman Resources Management and Development   ‚Ä¢ \nIntegrated Marketing   ‚Ä¢ \nManagement and Systems   ‚Ä¢ \nProfessional Writing   ‚Ä¢ \nProject Management   ‚Ä¢ \nPublic Relations and Corporate Comm.   ‚Ä¢ \nPublishing- Digital and Print Media   ‚Ä¢ \nReal Estate   ‚Ä¢ \nReal Estate Development   ‚Ä¢ \nSports Business   ‚Ä¢ \nTourism Management   ‚Ä¢ \nTranslation', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '1 212-998-7100', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, '$50', NULL, 'Spring / Summer / Fall', 'http://www.scps.nyu.edu/visit-us.html', 'https://www.facebook.com/NYUSPS/', 'https://twitter.com/nyusps', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/user/scpsnyu', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/scpsnyu', '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'NEW YORK UNIVERSITY - SPS', 'New York University-School of Professional Studies (NYU- SPS) is one of the highest ranking university in the US; usually within the 30 best universities!\n\nNew York University- SPS works exclusively with CollegeStudyUS for Graduate applications only for compensation. Effective for Fall, 2016, NYU is no longer offering compensation for any undergraduate applicant. NYU- SPS is one of the 15 major divisions of NYU and offers excellent Graduate degree programs not available in any other division of the university.\n\nNew York University (NYU) is the largest private university in the world with over 50,000 students and over 8,000 International students. It is one of the most popular universities in the United States and consistently ranks as one of the 30 most desired universities around the world. Located in New York City, the university offers international students unlimited opportunity to live and study in one of the most diverse cities in the world. \n\n', '\nNYU- SPS is one of the largest of the 15 divisions of NYU. Currently, almost 5,000 students attend NYU- SPS. Students receive the same grade transcripts and the same Graduation certificates as all other students at New York University.\n\nCollegeStudyUS has a special agreement with NYU''s School of Professional Studies (SPS) to offer Graduate and Undergraduate degree programs in a large number of academic areas and concentrations. NYU-SPS is a major division of the NYU system with over 5,000 students attending from all parts of the world.\n\nApplications- \nAll CSUS applicants can have the $150 application fee waived. For Graduate students the fee waiver is a multi-step process. All applications must be submitted on-line; no hard copies can be accepted. Almost all documents can be uploaded to the NYU, on-line application and then also to the CollgeStudyUS portal. Deadlines- October 1st for Spring entry and April 1st for Fall entry. Some programs accept students for Summer entry.\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
