(390, 'POST UNIVERSITY', 1890, 'USA', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/post-university.gif', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Post-University.jpg', 'Waterbury, CT , United States', '800 Country Club Rd, Waterbury, CT 06708, United States', NULL, 'Entrance Requirements- Undergraduates\n- Application For Admission \n- Official Transcripts- All previous schools (Minimum 2.75 on a 4.0 scale)\n- TOEFL (Minimum 80 ibt or 6.5 IELTS)\nLower scores, or no scores, considered for Conditional Admission\n- Personal Statement\n- 2 Letters of Recommendation\n- SAT or ACT scores are optional (If TOEFL/IELTS taken SAT may be\nwaived)\n- Copy of Passport\n\nEntrance Requirements- Transfer Undergraduates\n- Application For Admission (Application fee waived)\n- Official Transcripts- All previous universities (Minimum 3.0 on a 4.0 \nscale)\n- TOEFL (Minimum 79 ibt or 6.0 IELTS)\nLower scores, or no scores, considered for Conditional Admission\n- Personal Statement\n- Resume\n- 2 Letters of Recommendation\n- Copy of Passport\n\nTo receive an I-20-\n- File the required Tuition Deposit (via Credit Card)\n- Bank Statement (Dated within 90 days of Acceptance)\n- Affidavit of Support\n', 'Private', '$10,000', 'Accounting\nBiology/Biomedical Science\nBusiness Administration/Management\nChild Studies\nCriminal Justice\nEnvironmental Science/Studies\nEquine Business Management\nFinance\nHuman Services\nInformation Systems\nLegal Studies\nManagement\nMarketing\nPsychology\nSociology\nBusiness Administration/Management\nDrug and Alcohol Counseling\nMBA\nMental Health Clinician\n', 'Dr. Donald W. Mroz', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '1 800-660-6615', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, '$50', NULL, 'Spring / Summer / Fall', 'http://post.edu/?utm_source=googleplus&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=aboutsection', 'https://www.facebook.com/PostUniversity/', 'https://twitter.com/Postuniversity', 'https://plus.google.com/+postuniversity', 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/school?id=21132', 'https://www.instagram.com/postuniversity/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/postuniversity', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/postuniversity', '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'POST UNIVERSITY', 'Founded in 1890, Post University is a student-focused university committed to providing its 1000 students with the knowledge, skills and experience required to be leaders in their chosen fields. The university is located on 58 acres in Waterbury, Connecticut; a safe, scenic, friendly and convenient home for students. The Post campus in the middle of Connecticut and the area provides convenient service from Amtrak''s (train) Northeast Corridor as well as airline service to the state capital of Hartford. The campus is just 90 minutes away from New York City and two hours from Boston.\n\n', '\nPost offers a number of Undergraduate academic programs including: Business, Economics, Finance, Criminal Justice, Information Technology, Legal Studies, Sport Management, Equine Business Management, and Social Services. Campus life at Post University offers a wide range of cultural, educational, recreational, social, and athletic events and activities. The main Graduate program are MBA, MS Mental health and MS Drug & Alcohol Counseling program.\n\nThe student to faculty ratio is less than 15:1, which creates an ideal environment for daily interaction between students and their professors. Students at Post like the small classroom size and direct involvement with faculty. \n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
