(392, 'PURNELL SCHOLL- SECONDARY US HIGH SCHOOL', NULL, 'USA', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/pur.jpg', 'http://www.htir.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/purnell.jpg', '\nPottersville, NJ  ,United States', '51 Pottersville Rd., PO Box 500\nPottersville, NJ 07979 ,United States', NULL, NULL, 'Private', '$10,000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'On Campus/Off Campus', '1(908) 439.2154', 'admission@studymetro.com', NULL, '$50', NULL, 'Spring / Summer / Fall', 'https://www.purnell.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/purnellschool.org/', 'https://twitter.com/PurnellSchool?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.instagram.com/mypurnell/', NULL, NULL, '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'PURNELL SCHOLL- SECONDARY US HIGH SCHOOL', 'Purnell is an all girls'' high school (secondary school) for boarding and day school students with a tradition of serving young women for over 50 years. \n\nLocated just 1 hour from New York City in Pottersville, New Jersey the Purnell School campus provides a high quality education for young women in grades 9, 10, 11 and 12 as well as a post secondary program. Purnell is a place where young women can learn more about themselves, receive an excellent secondary education to prepare for university study, enhance their English language skills and reside on campus in a safe and secure environment. \n', '\nAn education at Purnell provides young women with daily support from their teachers, counselors, advisors and mentors to enhance their academic studies, co-curricular activities, athletics and residential life. Students have been quoted as saying, "Purnell is like a home. Here, teachers are not only teachers; they are our dorm parents and coaches. And everyone knows each other so well like sisters."\n\nThe Purnell School is also well equipped to assist students with learning differences.\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
