 the U.S. News & World Report.\nFarmingdale is the only public college in New York State offering the Aeronautical Science/Professional Pilot Bachelor Degree with 23 meticuloulsy maintained Piper and Cessna aircrafts.\nThe College has been ranked as one of the safest colleges in the U.S. by the online publication Daily Beast.\nFarmingdale has top-notch athletic facilities including a brand new eight lane all-weather track surrounding a synthetic turf soccer/lacrosse field, and a baseball stadium with lights and synthetic turf. Our teams have won seven Skyling Championships in the past four years. \nSeven of our programs have a 100% employment rate.\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
