com', NULL, '$50', NULL, 'Spring / Summer / Fall', 'http://suny.oneonta.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/SUNYOneonta', 'https://twitter.com/SUNY_Oneonta', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/edu/school?id=19037', 'https://www.instagram.com/sunyoneonta/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/SUNYOneonta', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/SUNYOneonta', '[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null]', NULL, 'SUNY - ONEONTA', 'SUNY Oneonta is a popular SUNY university and is a mid-size, public and has strong academic programs in many liberal arts and sciences areas. They prepare students for successful careers and the pursuit of advanced degrees.\n\nAs a member of the State University of New York (SUNY) system, Oneonta has small classes, opportunities for undergraduate research, and student/faculty interaction at a low, attractive cost for international students.\n\nLocated in the hills of Central New York state, the college''s idyllic setting is ideal for study, adventure and self-discovery. Just "up the hill" from the City of Oneonta, the campus blends community and academe to engage, nurture, and inspire.\n', 'Initially established in 1889 as a state normal school, Oneonta has become a premier school of the SUNY system. Their strong alumni network spans the globe, demonstrating the leadership and accomplishment that exemplify an Oneonta education.\n\nA beautiful natural environment, state-of-the-art facilities and a campus that''s just the right size make Oneonta a fantastic place to live and study. With a population of just under 14,000 people, Oneonta is a safe, friendly community known for its small-town ambiance and vibrant arts and entertainment scene.\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
